-- African Development Bank Gives Liberia $40 Million Water Grant
-- B y   E l i s e   Z o k e r
-- 2012-11-09T18:01:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-09/african-development-bank-gives-liberia-40-million-water-grant.html
The  African Development Bank  has
given a $40 million grant to the Liberia Water & Sewer Corp. to
improve water supplies in the region, Chairman Kimmie Weeks said
in Monrovia.  The Liberian company is revamping facilities in Monrovia
and towns in Lofa, Grand Gedeh and Margibi counties, Weeks said
yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elise Zoker in Johannesburg at 
